            <p class="mt-30px">
                I am pleased to inform you that you have been offered provisional admission into the Sandwich Programme for the award of B.Ed./B.Sc Degrees of
                the Nnamdi Azikiwe University with effect from @Model.Session.Name academic session in the Department of
                <span class="font-weight-bold px-10px "> @Model.Department.Name.ToUpper() </span>.
            </p>

            <p>
                i.  You will be required to produce the originals of all your claimed certificates and satisfy all the relevant entry requirements, before you are accorded
                full registration for the programme.
            </p>

            <p>
                ii. If at any time, after admission, it is discovered that you do not possess the qualification(s) on the basis of which you were offered provisional admission
                into the programme, you will be required to withdraw from the University.
            </p>

            <p>
                iii. You will abide by the university general and academic regulations as they affect student of the University.
            </p>

            <p>This offer of admission will lapse if it is not accepted one month after the commencement of registration.</p>

            <h4 class="font-weight-bold">ADDITIONAL INFORMATION</h4>
                <p>
                    On arrival at Nnamdi Azikiwe University, Awka you should proceed as follows:
                </p>
            <p>
                i. Report at the Admissions Office of the Sandwich Unit, with the originals and  photocopies of all your credentials for necessary clearance.
            </p>
            <p>
               ii. Thereafter proceed to the ICT section Sandwich Office for further briefing/course registration.
            </p>
            <p>Congratulations and best wishes.</p>
                <p class="pull-left">
